text.tspan: Command filter - you can put the fragment of command name, press Enter and active list will be filtered
Lists of commands loaded from files using "-f" option
(each tab contains commands from single file, name of tab can be put in command file)
List of commands from active tab (current or nex command is selected by ">")
Pressing (touching) command name will show its content at the bottom and also will copy it to clipboard
This button will not only copy command to clipboard but also paste it into Zellij active panel
and - if AutoExec is selected - will execute it (send Enter after pasting)
This will copy (and execute if AutoExec is on) "undo" command which can be optionally defined if file
Buttons:
When selected commands are pasted and executed in the current Zellij pane using
Right and Enter buttons.
When selected commands are pasted (but not executed) in the current Zellij
In this mode you need to also press Enter to execute them
"Right" - going down current command list
"Left" - going up current command list
"Enter" - submit command if pasted in the terminal
"Reset" - sends Ctrl-C to terminal
Changing active tab in Zellij terminal
Changing active pane in Zellij terminal

Clears Zellij terminal
Toogles full-screen for active Zellij pane
Toogles pane synchronized mode for active Zellij tab
